# -*-cperl-*-

=head1 NAME

_FTS2_INIT_

=head1 SYNOPSIS

_FTS2_INIT_

=head1 DESCRIPTION

This primitives initializes the source file to be processed by the FTS2 Data
Reduction engine.

=head1 OUTPUT FILES

Creates output files with a C<_fts> extension.
The Frame is updated with the output files.

=head1 NOTES

This primitive will operate on interferogram cubes.

=head1 AUTHOR

Coskun Oba E<lt> josh.oba@uleth.ca E<gt>

